{
  "id": "RAW_1d85c765",
  "title": "怎么用最小知识量掌握 AI 编程？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTEwNjI2MA==&mid=2651926190&idx=2&sn=8ee586891a92ae2468133219c4894b48",
  "date": "2026-04-08 23:46:00",
  "author": "人人都是产品经理",
  "siteName": "人人都是产品经理",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>张佳</span> <span>2026-04-09 07:46</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">广东</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=67bd67fe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibEdImMv0CQFPBEGiar0w0GEavXHThVhlgQsyczkg51quavwFDzo1sapqWL6JBb0OuQ3K5iccbr07lfibZMCAWriaRK2wtROqJacuF6gNA06HueM%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>它本是摆在所有人面前的机会，但是绝大多数人没看到。</p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;text-autospace: normal;text-align: left;color: #333333;background-color: #f9f9f7;font-family: Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, &quot;Songti SC&quot;, &quot;SimSun&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.7;padding: 1.25em 1em;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" class=\"js_darkmode__0\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 编程，绝对是此刻成为你人生拐点的最佳杠杆。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">它本是摆在所有人面前的机会，但是绝大多数人没看到。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">信息差这个东西，就是这么奇妙。</span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">我 2017 年的时候，跟几个小伙伴搭伙在工作之余做短视频，每周每个人都能跑一个 100 万粉丝的新号。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">就，毫无技术含量的从油管下载、转竖屏、发布，什么养号、限流、违规，都不存在。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样躺赚流量的事，我再次感知到是今年春节以后。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">我 Vibe-Coding 的一个开源项目</span></span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.875em;background-color: #f0f0ee;color: #111111;padding: 0.15em 0.35em;border: 1px solid #cccccc;\" class=\"js_darkmode__2\"><span leaf=\"\">Auto-Redbook-Skill</span></code><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">，一声不吭的噌噌的涨到了 1.6K Star</span></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 1em 0;text-align: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder js_darkmode__3\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100007285\" data-ratio=\"0.6037037037037037\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border: 1px solid #111111;display: block;margin: 0 auto;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=953a8133&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FM0M2LxLjvZiay4ick9DXibA3MtVIPRTsTPHTgH8ia1icRr1A97psmicWbjFPRroiaiad9nISpgVsib1y8F5M0PhBPia7QrMrmxqicAUSV8qiaSvgD6gbbiaI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D0\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">我曾参与运营过开源项目 Wechaty，有 22K 星标，由 54 个非常极客的程序员共同贡献、维护。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">在我负责项目社区运营的时候，它排在 GitHub 社区的前 500。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">按这个数据计算，我 Vibe-Coding 这个星标数对应的影响力，相当于一篇 10W+ 公众号文章。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">但我一个人，只花了一下午，就搞定了。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">这对于我这个非科班出身的开发者来说，在过去是想都不会想的。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">去年有一个华科大的大四学生，Vibe-Coding 了一个舆情项目</span></span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.875em;background-color: #f0f0ee;color: #111111;padding: 0.15em 0.35em;border: 1px solid #cccccc;\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\"><span leaf=\"\">BettaFish</span></code><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">，一个人、一周拿下了 10K 星标，然后拿到了意料之外的 Offer。</span></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 1em 0;text-align: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder js_darkmode__5\" data-ratio=\"0.7666666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border: 1px solid #111111;display: block;margin: 0 auto;\" data-imgfileid=\"100007281\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a3e7bc8d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FM0M2LxLjvZgjGDibeesAMaDWrCVql2socEJ8BMNRaxrkPZ5d0997LT4JNAZmpvuUq2auUvCWxkJx6JxnVVicvkJZoztUDcibI5xgpmQ14pSycc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">GitHub 上，非程序员、第一个项目就成为“人生爆款”冲上全球 Trending 的案例，比比皆是。</span></span>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">从萌生一个创意到落地为爆款，然后走上“人生巅峰”，可能就是半天的事儿。</span></span></span></strong></p>\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 1.25em 0px 0.4em;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-weight: 700;line-height: 1.2;font-size: 1.625em;color: rgb(26, 26, 26);padding-bottom: 0.25em;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(17, 17, 17);\" class=\"js_darkmode__7\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">门槛到底在哪？</span></span></h2>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">能看到这篇文章的你，绝对不是普通人，你一定也知道我上面所述的信息。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">你大概率已经上手试过了，</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是，</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">写出来的东西跟你开始兴奋的那个创意，</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">一点也不搭噶</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">。</span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">你甚至试图专门去学编程，</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是，</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">要学的东西似乎太太太太多了……</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">HTML、JavaScript、Python、Nodejs、环境变量、依赖、MySQL、终端、脚本……</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一大堆概念，每一个都非常有用，但每一个都那么难学。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">随便一个概念，打开一篇教程，就是一周的学习量。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">离谱。</span></span></span></strong></p>\n   <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 1em 0;text-align: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder js_darkmode__11\" data-ratio=\"0.6745932415519399\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"799\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100%;height:265px;border:1px solid #111111;display:block;margin:0 auto;width:393px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100007283\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=36b1ef3b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FM0M2LxLjvZhYHqgNJe9KclZTM9TXX2u67arQzh4Ria26zm5zJmbQuVOk68rWDxNVwwESvZibKaQZkhBiaCzzFKfG0GGBTFicricepL1cYQjMia4R8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是，如果你把这件事当成门槛，那就跑偏了。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天，任何直接往脑子里</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">垒知识</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">的行为，都是</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">大错特错</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">与 AI 协作一定要把&nbsp;</span></span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;font-size: 0.875em;background-color: #f0f0ee;color: #111111;padding: 0.15em 0.35em;border: 1px solid #cccccc;\" class=\"js_darkmode__14\"><span leaf=\"\">MVK</span></code><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这个词锁在脑子里。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">MVK 是 Minimum Viable Knowledge 的缩写，是我自创的词。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">它指的是，</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">要完成某项任务所需要的最小知识量</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">以 AI 编程为例：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你要开发一个可以在 Mac 电脑上运行的应用程序，那你需要知道的最小可行知识包括：</span></span></p>\n   <ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.9em;padding-left: 1.6em;list-style-type: decimal;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">知道 AI 写的代码是由一堆文档组成的，但不能通过双击任何一个文件运行；</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">知道 AI 写的代码需要使用指令打包成可点击运行的应用程序</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">知道使用 Nodejs 写的程序安装依赖时会有网络问题</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">知道如果程序没写好，运行时报错会输出在终端上</span></span></li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">其中的第 2、3 项，AI 大部分时候会帮你直接搞定。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">当你知道了第四条，你“开发”应用的效率会大大增加。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">是的，不需要知道任何 Nodejs 的语法，你只需要像一个“土老帽”一样跟 AI 说“我想体验一下这个程序，帮我搞定，然后告诉我怎么测试。”</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">但 AI 编程的 MVK 都有哪些呢？</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">你问到了问题的核心！(不是 Gemini 写的)</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">这才是真正的门槛：</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">你不知道会用到哪些知识，所以只能全学，但这又很扯淡。</span></span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">好在，我有多年低门槛把事干成的经验。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">我从 2024 年以来，已经 Vibe-Coding 100+个项目了。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">我除了做课、直播、交付之外的时间，几乎都在折腾 Cursor 帮我实现各种各样的创意。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">我还给 Kimi 和阶跃的开源项目贡献过代码。</span></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 1em 0;text-align: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder js_darkmode__17\" data-ratio=\"0.6675925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border: 1px solid #111111;display: block;margin: 0 auto;\" data-imgfileid=\"100007282\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7635b64&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FM0M2LxLjvZhDYng5ybjvbccFLTRyb9A5TWbg1So1KHbPgAdicGcu6I3NBTgFvibmibqC2ttD44OfuMF1YvzHr2YNTkdho7FicOOgJsULpCe72ko%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D3\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">网页应用、浏览器插件、脚本程序、App、客户端应用、CLI、Agent、Skills，这些热门的 AI 编程落地方向，我都折腾过一遍了。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">我把他们都打包了，但不是给你个视频/文章/教程，你闷头去学。</span></span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 1.25em 0px 0.4em;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-weight: 700;line-height: 1.2;font-size: 1.625em;color: rgb(26, 26, 26);padding-bottom: 0.25em;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(17, 17, 17);\" class=\"js_darkmode__18\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">咋学呢？</span></span></h2>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span leaf=\"\">“干中学。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">去年电视剧《漂白》中的爆梗，放在这里最合适了。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">还是那句话，任何直接往脑子里</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">垒知识</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">的行为，都是</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">大错特错</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">你的脑子应该流出足够多的空间，以方便它萌生创意，而不是垒满了知识。</span></span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">实际上，我们学习的大部分知识，都是“日抛型”的，完全没必要把它们存下来。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 在手，天下知识技能我都有。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">认识不到这一点，就白生在这个好时代了。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">不要为了学习而学习，要为了解决问题而学习。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 AI 编程里，</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">报错信息是最好的教材</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">在跟 AI 沟通过程中，它冒出来的各种新关键词，都立刻让 AI 给你讲清楚、了解它的应用场景。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">Just-in-Time</span>，用-问-学，持续有用的存下来、没用的立刻扔掉。</span></span></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 1em 0;text-align: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder js_darkmode__24\" data-ratio=\"0.725925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100%;height:176px;border:1px solid #111111;display:block;margin:0 auto;width:242px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100007284\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f8632124&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FM0M2LxLjvZhLNvIzoKCicEJetUy5WiaVxRnlVPpyByHHmq9tcVEJFXPLjhQkYuR2OiaGceCK4crM1IZknJoCB8Y1H9HAXjIBmSIXkInxaHgAI4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D4\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 1.25em 0px 0.4em;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-weight: 700;line-height: 1.2;font-size: 1.625em;color: rgb(26, 26, 26);padding-bottom: 0.25em;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(17, 17, 17);\" class=\"js_darkmode__25\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">从哪开始</span></span></h2>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">OK，第二个门槛来了。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我还没有创意，但是想赶紧拥有这个杠杆。”</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">我把过去 Vibe-Coding 那 100+ 个项目的所有 MVK 做了一个系统性梳理，搞了个“干中学行动路径”。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">~10 个项目，覆盖应用程序的主流形态，并且是此刻最热门的：</span></span></p>\n   <ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box;mar