leaf=\"\">花 3 周时间，把这些项目走一遍，所有必备知识点就集齐了：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">第一周：快速上手</span></span></span></strong></p>\n   <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.9em;padding-left: 1.6em;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">找到趁手的 AI 编程工具</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">开发个人作品集网页</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">开发一个浏览器插件</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">开发批处理 Excel 的 Python 程序</span></span></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">学完你就知道 HTML/CSS/JS/Python 都是干嘛的，终端怎么用，报错怎么调。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">第二周：专业进阶</span></span></span></strong></p>\n   <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.9em;padding-left: 1.6em;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">开发引入 AI 的网页应用（搞懂 API、JSON、Key）</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">开发 AI 数据分析 Agent</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">为网页增加账号系统（搞懂数据库）</span></span></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">学完你就能接入 AI 能力、玩转 Nodejs、开发有后台管理的完整产品。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">第三周：高阶跃迁</span></span></span></strong></p>\n   <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.9em;padding-left: 1.6em;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">用 Git 做版本管理，活用 GitHub</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">开发 OpenClaw Mini 版</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">开发 Agent 能用的 Skills &amp; CLI</span></span></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">把产品封装成各种客户端、Docker 镜像</span></span></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">每周更新基础项目视频课程，外加数个延伸扩展项目直播。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">跟着“干”完，AI 编程杠杆就轻松为你所用了。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">详细项目和知识点安排，扫码落地页整起吧。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;font-weight: 700;color: #111111;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">提醒：现在报名，可以赶上直播带教。</span></span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;overflow-wrap: break-word;margin-bottom: 0.9em;text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-character;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">4 月前后都是假期，与其干啥都没状态浪费时间，学点或许能“改命”的本事吧。</span></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 1em 0;text-align: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder js_darkmode__30\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"512\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100%;height:220px;border:1px solid #111111;display:block;margin:0 auto;width:220px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100007286\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2e032d38&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FM0M2LxLjvZjNIrWOHRE4vJicRQqqqmc7uz8D0FNadEkgOlSxFa8W9rIZMiaQVrJXnmFREOzRIAWn5LhA6UJPygEXBvuoTe52jnvvzIjLvDM6s%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D5\"></span>\n   </figure>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=604ace83&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMjM5OTEwNjI2MA%3D%3D%26mid%3D2651926190%26idx%3D2%26sn%3D8ee586891a92ae2468133219c4894b48\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文提出「最小可行知识（MVK）」理念，主张通过「干中学」的 Vibe-Coding 模式，让非科班人员以极低门槛快速落地 AI 编程项目。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文提出「最小可行知识（MVK）」理念，主张通过「干中学」的 Vibe-Coding 模式，让非科班人员以极低门槛快速落地 AI 编程项目。",
  "summary": "文章探讨了在 AI 时代非技术人员如何通过 AI 编程实现职业突破。作者提出了「最小可行知识（Minimum Viable Knowledge， MVK）」的概念，强调不应盲目堆砌编程基础知识，而应聚焦于完成特定任务所需的最小知识集。通过分享个人从非科班背景到实现多个高星开源项目的经历，作者提倡「干中学（Just-in-Time）」的学习模式，即以解决问题为导向，在报错和实践中即时学习。文章最后提供了一套为期三周的行动路径，涵盖网页应用、插件、脚本及 Agent 开发等热门方向，旨在帮助读者快速掌握 AI 编程杠杆。",
